{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.120", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren auf der Trib\u00fcne! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.720", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Antr\u00e4ge von Linken und Gr\u00fcnen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.040", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wurde bereits gesagt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind nicht neu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.640", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und so bleibt es auch bei unserer Antwort: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.640", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir lehnen die Anhebung des Mindestalters bei der Bundeswehr auf 18\u00a0Jahre ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.480", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie argumentieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.800", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Fraktion der Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor allen Dingen mit den brutalen Vorkommnissen und Erfahrungen aus der Horrorwelt von Krieg und Gewalt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese gibt es; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.800", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist richtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.120", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Geschildert wurden auch dieser Tage wieder Schicksale von Heranwachsenden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.440", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die verschleppt und als Kindersoldaten zum Kriegsdienst gezwungen wurden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.600", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sind furchtbare Schicksale von Hunderttausenden von Kindern und Jugendlichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.000", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir tats\u00e4chlich verhindern m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.200", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesrepublik engagiert sich hier auch vollkommen zu Recht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch was hat dies mit jungen Rekruten in der Bundeswehr zu tun?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.560", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage Ihnen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.520", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "rein gar nichts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.000", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Deutschland wird kein Kind und kein Jugendlicher in den Milit\u00e4rdienst verschleppt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.080", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er oder sie ist mindestens 17\u00a0Jahre alt und wird vor der freiwillig zu bekundenden Teilnahme intensiv beraten und vorbereitet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.520", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf physische sowie mentale Tauglichkeit getestet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.840", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor allem m\u00fcssen die Eltern dem Dienst in der Bundeswehr zustimmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.800", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Familienpolitikerin ist mir dies besonders wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.480", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eltern kennen n\u00e4mlich ihr Kind und k\u00f6nnen in diesem Alter noch zu-, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.840", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch abraten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.960", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.920", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da bin ich mir sicher\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.240", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie nehmen diese Verantwortung sehr ernst."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch wenn die Eltern zustimmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.640", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "darf dieser junge Mensch bis zur Vollj\u00e4hrigkeit keinen bewaffneten Dienst aus\u00fcben oder gar in einen Auslandseinsatz geschickt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.440", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er kann in der Probezeit seinen Dienst jeden Tag sofort quittieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist die in Ihren Antrag eingearbeitete Beschreibung von Zust\u00e4nden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen Kinder und Jugendliche\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich zitiere\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201egewaltbasierte Handlungsstrategien bis hin zum T\u00f6ten anderer Menschen erlernen und eigene Gewalterfahrungen machen\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.400", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "suggestiv, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "irreal und absolut nicht angebracht;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.320", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn davon erleben 17-J\u00e4hrige im Dienst der Bundeswehr nichts."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.440", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die neurowissenschaftlichen Erkenntnisse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.440", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie ins Feld f\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.600", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "besagen nichts: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.160", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen unter 20\u00a0Jahre h\u00e4tten noch kein vollausgebildetes Hirn und seien deshalb nicht in der Lage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dramatische Erfahrungen zu verarbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.920", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Sch\u00f6ne ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.560", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere jungen Rekruten wachsen nicht in Kriegsgebieten auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.760", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sie kommen auch nicht dorthin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "solange sie minderj\u00e4hrig sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die\u00a0Gr\u00fcnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.960", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "selbst Ihr Argument im Antrag kann nicht verfangen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.760", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unser Engagement gegen die Beteiligung von Kindern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.760", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also von bis zu 14-J\u00e4hrigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.920", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an bewaffneten Konflikten w\u00e4re nur dann glaubw\u00fcrdig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir die Rekrutierung von Minderj\u00e4hrigen in unserem Land gesetzlich verb\u00f6ten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.680", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber was hat das mit der Ausbildung von 17-J\u00e4hrigen unter den beschriebenen vorbildlichen Bedingungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.200", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gro\u00dfartigem Jugendschutz und besonderer F\u00fcrsorge der Bundeswehr zu tun? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wiederum rein gar nichts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.080", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Also kann unser Umgang mit dem Thema unserer Arbeit in den Gremien der UN und anderswo gar nicht im Wege stehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn Sie von Glaubw\u00fcrdigkeit sprechen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.800", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich will Ihnen Ihre Absicht nat\u00fcrlich nicht absprechen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.720", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Antr\u00e4ge eben nicht so glaubw\u00fcrdig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.720", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie r\u00fccken die dramatische Lage in anderen Weltgegenden bewusst in die N\u00e4he der ganz anderen Realit\u00e4t an hiesigen Ausbildungsorten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht ist es aber auch so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es dem einen oder anderen einfach nicht gef\u00e4llt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.280", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Bundeswehr aktiv um den Eintritt qualifizierter junger Leute bem\u00fcht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.360", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sonst woanders lernen und arbeiten w\u00fcrden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.840", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht sind Sie an einer einsatzf\u00e4higen und personell gut ausgestatteten Bundeswehr auch gar nicht so sehr interessiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Union und weite Teile des Hauses stehen zur Bundeswehr als Parlamentsarmee, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.880", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcberwacht und gef\u00fchrt durch Institutionen unseres demokratischen Rechtsstaats, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.920", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem sie Rechenschaft ablegen muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.120", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt keine Wehrpflicht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.200", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie ist ausgesetzt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.720", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und keine Zwangsrekrutierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.880", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es gibt einen sehr guten Jugendschutz f\u00fcr die kleine Gruppe noch minderj\u00e4hriger Rekruten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.400", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Letzter Satz: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.520", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr darf daher nicht dem Vergleich mit kinderraubenden B\u00fcrgerkriegsarmeen ausgesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.640", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Vergleich schadet ihrem Ansehen und schm\u00e4lert ihren Auftrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.840", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der unsere Sicherheit ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.720", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank f\u00fcr Ihre Aufmerksamkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.160", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.200", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Wiesmann.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.960", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chstes erteile ich das Wort der Abgeordneten Ulrike Bahr von der SPD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}